{
  "texts": [
    "Our screening strategy comprised four steps for selecting relevant articles.",
    "In the identification step, 5546 papers were sourced from heterogeneous databases.",
    "The titles and abstracts of the extracted articles were reviewed to ensure there was no repetition, as it is common for an article to be published in one venue (journals or conferences) and also on a preprint server, such as arXiv, to gain more visibility, citations, and feedback.",
    "Additionally, we ensured that the selected papers were related to IDS in FL settings.",
    "However, since the title and abstract alone may not provide a clear reflection of the paper, we proceeded to the screening step, where the titles, abstracts, and full texts of the articles were reviewed."
  ]
}